title: Labtec Webcam 5.1.0  Drivers made from the original CD: 171MB
description:
Labtec Webcam 5.1.0  Drivers made from the original CD: 171MB
LABTEC Camera M/N V-UAE13
 

Windows 9X to Windows 2000/XP this has no Vista Support! 

This is a Zip file of the original CD. which after searching for this file myself, without success. 

 I found the original CD  in a pile of CD&#039;s, Zipped that CD and posted it online for others.           

 If you are able to host this file and distribute it free, please do so. 
 

If you only want to install the driver, or having problems installing, once file is downloaded and unzipped, follow the direction below.

This is For XP: Once you plug in the camera and New Hardware Found Message  displays, search for driver manually and  open the folder  WinDrv2, this is the correct location for the XP driver. 

The Main setup.exe installs the software and the driver. This doesn&#039;t always work on the first try. 

If you have Vista, save yourself the headaches and buy a new camera that is compatible, or try the .ini file!


Good Luck
